{
  "description": "DeciContas — Brazilian legal NER dataset of audit-court rulings (TCE/RN). Four entity classes: MULTA (fines), OBRIGACAO (obligations), RESSARCIMENTO (refunds), RECOMENDACAO (recommendations). 861 documents (after filtering 5 few-shot leakage cases from the original 866-doc Label Studio export).",
  "license": "see dataset/release/README.md",
